      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我盯着礼物，纠结要不要送给她。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_022",
      "target_id": "sent_022",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "走出书店后想起她的生日，又回头看了一眼。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_023",
      "target_id": "sent_023",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我觉得相机太贵不买，平板太贵不买，滑板太贵不买，但游戏不贵就买了，忍不住笑了。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_024",
      "target_id": "sent_024",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "想到她和游戏，我还是去结账吧。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": ""
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_025",
